text: Dog Soldiers is a 2002 British American Luxembourgian horror movie directed by the first time director Neil Marshall and starring Sean Pertwee, Kevin McKidd, Emma Cleasby, Liam Cunningham, Thomas Lockyer, Darren Morfitt.
